y Scholar Archive, a comprehensive repository dedicated to storing articles, researches, and lectures produced by students and faculty members. Our archive serves as a platform for sharing valuable knowledge and insights in the fields of Genetic Algorithm, Game Theory, and Matching Theory.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Mission</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Hanoi University Faculty of Information and Technology, we are committed to fostering academic excellence and innovation in the field of information technology. Our Scholar Archive is an extension of this commitment, providing a centralized hub for accessing a diverse range of scholarly works produced by our community.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What We Offer</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our archive features a wealth of resources covering various aspects of Genetic Algorithm, Game Theory, and Matching Theory. Whether you\'re a student, researcher, or enthusiast, you\'ll find valuable content that explores theoretical concepts, practical applications, and cutting-edge developments in these fields.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Articles:</strong> Explore in-depth articles authored by students and faculty members, covering topics such as algorithm optimization, strategic decision-making, and mathematical modeling.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Researches:</strong> Access research papers that delve into specific areas of interest within Genetic Algorithm, Game Theory, and Matching Theory. Discover the latest findings and advancements shaping the future of these disciplines.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Lectures:</strong> Enhance your understanding of key concepts through recorded lectures delivered by experts in the field. Our archive hosts a collection of educational materials designed to supplement classroom learning and foster intellectual curiosity.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contributing to the Archive</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Are you a student or faculty member interested in contributing to our archive? We welcome submissions of original research papers, articles, and lecture materials related to Genetic Algorithm, Game Theory, and Matching Theory. By sharing your work with our community, you\'ll help enrich our collective knowledge and promote interdisciplinary collaboration.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Get Involved</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join us in exploring the fascinating world of Genetic Algorithm, Game Theory, and Matching Theory. Whether you\'re conducting research, seeking inspiration, or simply expanding your horizons, the Hanoi University Faculty of Information and Technology Scholar Archive is here to support your academic journey.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank you for visiting, and we hope you enjoy exploring our archive!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About','','publish','closed','closed','','about','','','2024-03-05 12:01:16','2024-03-05 12:01:16','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=17',4,'page','',0),(18,1,'2024-02-23 10:54:18','2024-02-23 10:54:18','','Elementor #17','','inherit','closed','closed','','17-revision-v1','','','2024-02-23 10:54:18','2024-02-23 10:54:18','',17,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=18',0,'revision','',0),(19,1,'2024-02-23 10:58:15','2024-02-23 10:58:15','','Elementor #17','','inherit','closed','closed','','17-revision-v1','','','2024-02-23 10:58:15','2024-02-23 10:58:15','',17,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=19',0,'revision','',0),(20,1,'2024-02-23 10:5